{"tid":1147482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑多番行錯路 DC9聽港女「導航」發火︰我有分數","createTime":"2019-05-10T01:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T01:46:35.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eeb4e042ccde22a2ded1daecb61cccdbf3bba7a1","tid":1147482,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T01:00:05.000Z","msg":"疑多番行錯路 的哥聽港女「導航」發火︰我有分數<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HatruV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HatruV&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=fbabe683\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HatruV</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190510/photo/bkn-20190510083023002-0510_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190510083350\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190510%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190510083023002-0510_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190510083350&h=a06c3da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該網民於周四（9日）在Facebook群組「香港的士違法關注組」發貼指，她一上車已指明路線，惟眼見司機疑因不熟路走錯，她雖再三「人肉導航」，但司機仍行錯路兼發惡罵人。<br />\n<br />\n影片可見，司機怒氣沖沖地質問：「你熟定我熟呀？我有我嘅路線行，我點會唔知邊條路打邊條路」，更怒罵：「唔鍾意就落車！車喺我手上，我鍾意行邊條路嘅，我有分數」。<br />\n<br />\n女乘客聞言氣定神閒地回應：「我只係好禮貌地話畀你聽係可以咁行，我亦都冇鬧你&hellip;但你可以話畀我聽嘛&hellip;不過唔重要，兩條路都行到啫」。"},{"pid":"0411df3294fd33c7a964d07c273428905db5f67e","tid":1147482,"uid":57844,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T01:06:17.000Z","msg":"注意呢個樓主歷史上只轉載新聞，仲要係東方<br />\n絕對係記者acc 呃hit rate"},{"pid":"aba09b3aa12634576983af3736006413014db937","tid":1147482,"uid":130901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T01:12:57.000Z","msg":"懶有禮貌咁，比人兜緊路呃錢呀on9<br />\n話即刻落車係咪唔收錢"},{"pid":"f0e066e6b9b81dc16b47be0a260d3ca16e54af5d","tid":1147482,"uid":205844,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T01:13:09.000Z","msg":"諗起個女人把閪聲一定好撚柒煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935958009fe808a3e67cbff110fc98a00075cf83","tid":1147482,"u